Card is accepted at a wide variety of stores and online sites. Once you load the prepaid card, you're ready to go! You can either purchase online, buy in-store using the card or even use your mobile phones in purchasing at stores that are NFC –enabled. 
												
 Easy Access to Funds 
Prepaid card is reloadable. We offer numerous ways for you to load it. Once loaded, you can easily access the funds using Nexus Wallet – do as many transactions (Send Money, Mobile Top Up, Pay Bills, Send Funds) and even withdraw cash at ATM machines.  
												

Prepaid card is part of the MoneyPass Network which enables any cardholder to make withdrawals at over 20,000 ATMS nationwide. 

 Worry-free transactions 
You'll never run into the risk of incurring debt because your transaction will always depend on the funds available on your card. Plus our secure and fraud-proof system guarantees peace of mind with every transaction you do with either the card or inside Nexus Wallet.. 

												
 Real-time bill payment confirmation 
Nexus Wallet gives you email/sms confirmation once payment has successfully push through. No more wondering if your bill is paid. 
												




