NexusFunds
Nexus Wallet allows you to connect with other Nexus Wallet owners by giving you the ability to transfer funds directly and safely to their wallet. You can send up to $500 for every transfer to other Nexus Wallet accountholders. This instantly reflects on their account balance where they can also perform various Nexus Wallet options.


