NexusFunds
Connectivity should not end in conversations on mobile phones – Nexus Wallet allows you to connect with other Nexus Wallet owners by giving you the power to transfer funds safely to them.
				


You can send up to $500 per transfer to other Nexus Wallet holder. This instantly instantly reflects on their account balance where they have choice to do anything!
				


Transaction happens instantaneously. When you transfer funds, it quickly instantly reflects on their account balance. NO DELAY. 
Just like any funds in Nexus Wallet, the transfer recipient has the flexibility to use it anywhere he wants. It goes directly to his mobile wallet app, and Prepaid Card. He even has the option to withdraw it from an ATM machine 
You have the full option to either accept or decline a NEXUSFUND transaction. No transfer will happen without your consent and approval so you remain in control of everything!
				




